[
  {
    "text": "Your Nick Jr. friends are great finders.",
    "start": 0.292,
    "duration": 3.045
  },
  {
    "text": "I see something!",
    "start": 3.462,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Can you spot the difference\nin these Nick Jr. moments?",
    "start": 4.796,
    "duration": 2.795
  },
  {
    "text": "Look carefully, there will be\nthree differences in each scene.",
    "start": 7.674,
    "duration": 3.546
  },
  {
    "text": "Get those eyes ready.\nLet's go!",
    "start": 11.303,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "First, it's the PAW Patrol.",
    "start": 14.264,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Nothing like relaxing on the beach.",
    "start": 16.892,
    "duration": 2.377
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, Rubble, no time to relax.",
    "start": 20.812,
    "duration": 2.378
  },
  {
    "text": "I need you on team Chase.",
    "start": 23.398,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "Team Skye is still gonna win.",
    "start": 25.943,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey Skye, you forgot something.",
    "start": 28.487,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "The ball!",
    "start": 31.114,
    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "There's a difference.\nWhat's that boat doing there?",
    "start": 32.074,
    "duration": 3.336
  },
  {
    "text": "That boat definitely doesn't\nbelong in Adventure Bay.",
    "start": 35.494,
    "duration": 3.462
  },
  {
    "text": "Be on the look out\nfor the next difference.",
    "start": 40.874,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "Sweet save, Marshall.",
    "start": 44.336,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh look, those are traffic cones\nin one scene,",
    "start": 47.673,
    "duration": 4.129
  },
  {
    "text": "but buckets in the other. Nice!",
    "start": 51.885,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "Now where's that third difference?",
    "start": 54.513,
    "duration": 2.461
  },
  {
    "text": "She scores!",
    "start": 57.432,
    "duration": 1.419
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah! Way to go Skye!",
    "start": 58.934,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa!",
    "start": 61.186,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Did that count as a goal too?",
    "start": 63.021,
    "duration": 2.211
  },
  {
    "text": "And there's the third! The bucket\non Marshall's head is blue there,",
    "start": 65.274,
    "duration": 4.045
  },
  {
    "text": "and red here, great job!",
    "start": 69.403,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "You found all three differences\nin the PAW Patrol scene.",
    "start": 72.155,
    "duration": 3.504
  },
  {
    "text": "Next is Blue's Clues and You.",
    "start": 76.702,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Three differences to find, let's look!",
    "start": 78.912,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasping]",
    "start": 81.206,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, how about these?",
    "start": 82.583,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you see another difference?",
    "start": 85.377,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, where do grapes grow?",
    "start": 87.296,
    "duration": 2.794
  },
  {
    "text": "Got it! The Felt Friends,\nFred and Felicia,",
    "start": 90.174,
    "duration": 3.461
  },
  {
    "text": "are wearing different colors.",
    "start": 93.76,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "Fred's shirt is orange and\nFelicia's shirt is purple.",
    "start": 95.888,
    "duration": 3.962
  },
  {
    "text": "But what color are their shirts here?",
    "start": 99.975,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right.\nHere, Fred's shirt is green,",
    "start": 102.644,
    "duration": 3.504
  },
  {
    "text": "and Felicia's shirt is red.",
    "start": 106.231,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "- Good eye.\n- Where do grapes grow?",
    "start": 108.483,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Where do grapes grow?",
    "start": 114.907,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "On a vine!",
    "start": 120.245,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Get ready, there's another\ndifference coming up.",
    "start": 121.33,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "[barking]",
    "start": 124.875,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "[barking]",
    "start": 127.252,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "On a vine!",
    "start": 130.339,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you find the second difference?",
    "start": 131.59,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right, look!\nThis tree has oranges,",
    "start": 134.551,
    "duration": 3.629
  },
  {
    "text": "but what's on this tree?",
    "start": 138.305,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right, apples.",
    "start": 140.891,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "Good job.",
    "start": 142.726,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Grapes grow on vines, yeah!",
    "start": 144.228,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep looking.\nThere's one more difference.",
    "start": 147.564,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Oranges grow on trees, on trees\nOranges grow on trees ♪",
    "start": 150.567,
    "duration": 2.962
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Potatoes grow down, down in the ground\nThey grow down in the ground ♪",
    "start": 153.612,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ We grapes we grow on vines on vines\nIn bunches we grow on vines on vines ♪",
    "start": 156.615,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ In big ol' bunches\nOn vines, on vines, on vines ♪",
    "start": 159.993,
    "duration": 2.545
  },
  {
    "text": "One more time.",
    "start": 162.955,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Oranges grow on trees, on trees ♪",
    "start": 164.54,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait a minute. Did you see that?",
    "start": 166.166,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And there's the last difference.",
    "start": 169.002,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Magenta is hiding in this scene.\nHi, Magenta!",
    "start": 171.129,
    "duration": 3.212
  },
  {
    "text": "Great job!",
    "start": 174.383,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "One more time.",
    "start": 175.467,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Oranges grow on trees, on trees\nOranges grow on trees ♪",
    "start": 177.052,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's do another.",
    "start": 180.013,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, it's Peppa Pig.",
    "start": 181.598,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "And I will play my drum.",
    "start": 183.684,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Mummy Pig plays the violin.",
    "start": 185.853,
    "duration": 1.876
  },
  {
    "text": "Daddy Pig plays the accordion.",
    "start": 188.981,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Peppa plays the drum.",
    "start": 192.192,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "You found the first difference? Where?",
    "start": 194.444,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right, the couch\nis a different color.",
    "start": 197.447,
    "duration": 3.421
  },
  {
    "text": "Here the couch is purple,\nbut what color is this one?",
    "start": 200.993,
    "duration": 4.713
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right, it's yellow.\nNice work!",
    "start": 206.665,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "Can you find another.",
    "start": 210.085,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "But what instrument will George play?",
    "start": 212.88,
    "duration": 1.918
  },
  {
    "text": "[music playing]",
    "start": 214.882,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "[horn blowing]",
    "start": 218.677,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Another difference, good job!",
    "start": 221.346,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "That painting in the background\nis different.",
    "start": 224.308,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "[horn blowing]",
    "start": 227.519,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "[horn blowing]",
    "start": 230.856,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "[giggling]",
    "start": 232.399,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "George is blowing the horn.",
    "start": 233.525,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Mummy couldn't play the horn.",
    "start": 235.861,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "And Daddy couldn't play it,\nand even I couldn't play it.",
    "start": 238.197,
    "duration": 4.504
  },
  {
    "text": "But George can play it!",
    "start": 243.368,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you see the last difference?",
    "start": 245.329,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes, there it is!",
    "start": 248.957,
    "duration": 1.544
  },
  {
    "text": "George's horn looks different.",
    "start": 251.335,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "[horn blowing]",
    "start": 253.212,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "[horn blowing]",
    "start": 257.174,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "[music playing]",
    "start": 258.884,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "[horn blowing]",
    "start": 269.394,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 270.771,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Last one. It's our Bubble Guppies friends.",
    "start": 274.525,
    "duration": 2.877
  },
  {
    "text": "Think you can find\nall three differences?",
    "start": 277.653,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "Excuse me.",
    "start": 285.577,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait a minute. Did you see that?",
    "start": 286.578,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "That screen was playing\nBlue's Clues and You.",
    "start": 289.206,
    "duration": 2.628
  },
  {
    "text": "Good job!",
    "start": 291.917,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Excuse me.",
    "start": 293.544,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "What time is it?",
    "start": 295.921,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "It's time for lunch!",
    "start": 297.464,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ What time is it?\nIt's time for lunch! ♪",
    "start": 299.967,
    "duration": 2.043
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ What time is it?\nIt's time for lunch! ♪",
    "start": 302.094,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ What time is it?\nIt's time for lunch! ♪",
    "start": 304.096,
    "duration": 1.918
  },
  {
    "text": "- It's lunchtime!\n- Get ready.",
    "start": 306.098,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "There's another difference coming up.",
    "start": 307.307,
    "duration": 2.086
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey Agent Oona,\nwhat did you get for lunch today?",
    "start": 309.476,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "I got a veggie burger\nwith barbecue sauce.",
    "start": 313.105,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "What did you get, Agent Goby?",
    "start": 316.024,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "I got a cheese burger with spicy sauce.",
    "start": 318.652,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "What did you get, Agent Nonny?",
    "start": 321.446,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "A got a burger with..",
    "start": 323.657,
    "duration": 2.794
  },
  {
    "text": "Secret sauce?",
    "start": 326.618,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "Be on the look out\nfor the next difference.",
    "start": 328.078,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "Secret Sauce?",
    "start": 330.205,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "That's silly.",
    "start": 331.79,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "And secret.",
    "start": 333.584,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, you got another one.",
    "start": 336.17,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Goby's lunch box is\nsupposed to be green,",
    "start": 338.005,
    "duration": 2.752
  },
  {
    "text": "but what's that color?",
    "start": 340.883,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right, that's yellow.",
    "start": 343.76,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "What brings you to our secret\nhideout, Agent Nonny?",
    "start": 346.263,
    "duration": 2.586
  },
  {
    "text": "I have some very important\nmessages for you from Mr. G.",
    "start": 348.974,
    "duration": 2.961
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep looking, there's one more.",
    "start": 352.019,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "- Agent Oona.\n- Thank you.",
    "start": 354.229,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "- Agent Goby.\n- Thanks.",
    "start": 356.231,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "[barking.",
    "start": 358.192,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you find another one?",
    "start": 362.946,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right, the envelopes\nhave a different picture on them.",
    "start": 365.949,
    "duration": 3.879
  },
  {
    "text": "You're so good at this!",
    "start": 369.953,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Good job spotting those differences.\nWhich round was your favorite?",
    "start": 372.247,
    "duration": 4.463
  },
  {
    "text": "You can ask your parents to subscribe\nto the Nick Jr. YouTube channel",
    "start": 376.919,
    "duration": 3.378
  },
  {
    "text": "for new videos every day.",
    "start": 380.38,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "And find more of your favorite\nshows on TV",
    "start": 382.09,
    "duration": 2.128
  },
  {
    "text": "on Nickelodeon and the Nick Jr. channel.",
    "start": 384.301,
    "duration": 2.419
  }
]